OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly fog clearing, then dry
OL,6,Fand very mild with warm sunny spells
OL,7,Fduring Wednesday. Winds slowly ease
OL,8,Fthroughout the day but remaining
OL,9,Fbreezy along the coast.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FBecoming increasingly cloudy
OL,12,Fovernight with patchy light rain and
OL,13,Fdrizzle with low cloud. Light winds
OL,14,Fbut blustery along the coast.
OL,15,
OL,16,CThursday:FTurning breezy with some
OL,17,Fsunny intervals during the morning.
OL,18,FCloudy with light rain or showers
OL,19,Fduring the afternoon, becoming more
OL,20,Fpersistent and heavier overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
